            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/23053",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Assigning to Thomas.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-07-24T19:46:20.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-07-24T19:46:20.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/23154",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "For your information:\nThis is not a bug of Zend_Translate.\n\nWhen gettext files are compiled with poEdit the editor adds it's own information as translation of an empty string. ALL translations are used and returned, of course also an empty translation.\n\nSo the general question is:\n\nDo we want to suppress the informations when they are provided ?\nOr do we change Zend_Form to \"not translate\" empty strings.\n\nSuppressing the informations raise another possible problems... other editors could add such information in a different translation. As mentioned this is a poEdit ONLY problem which adds this information as translation for an empty string.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-07-28T12:44:23.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-07-28T12:44:23.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/23155",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "As Thomas notes, this is not a bug in Zend_Translate, and Zend_Translate is only doing Zend_Form's bidding; ultimately, it's a poEdit issue.\n\nI'm closing this, as there's no reasonable solution on the framework side.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-07-28T12:51:03.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-07-28T12:51:03.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/23158",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "New feature implemented with r10517.\n\nEmpty translations are now suppressed by the gettext adapter.\nAdapter informations can be retrieved with the new 'getAdapterInfo()' method.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-07-28T13:40:04.000+0000",
